  m_text: "This is the haptic interface, did you notice that your hands are gone?
    Take the stylus out from the haptic device in the re\tal world, you should see
    it following your movement in the virtual environment. To write, you can just
    write like it's pen and paper. When you're satisfied with your writing, use the
    pen to press the \"take screenshot\" button. You can look at your artistry in
    the framed picture to your left. If you're satisfied with your writing, press
    \"scan screenshot\" to send it to the model. To go to the next interface, press
    the button on the stylus closest to the tip."
